OL,3,CFrom the newsroom to the farm: A
OL,4,Cweekend lambing in Somerset
OL,6,FI grew up on a farm in North Yorkshire
OL,7,Fand my favourite part of the year was
OL,8,Flambing. I would always spend the half
OL,9,Fterm holiday helping, and then go as
OL,10,Fmuch as I could alongside school.
OL,11,FEvery chance I had - I was there.
OL,13,FFast forward a few years and I work
OL,14,Fbehind the scenes at ITV West Country,
OL,15,Fbut when the opportunity came up to go
OL,16,Flambing on a farm in Somerset, I
OL,17,Fcouldn't resist.
