OL,3,CFrom the newsroom to the farm: A
OL,4,Cweekend lambing in Somerset
OL,6,FI headed to Cheddar for a couple of
OL,7,Fdays to join Rosie Bloor on her farm.
OL,8,FShe has a flock lambing indoors and
OL,9,Foutdoors.
OL,11,FNow that we are into the warmer
OL,12,Fmonths, although definitely not drier,
OL,13,Fthe option of outdoor lambing is
OL,14,Fsomething many farmers choose to do,
OL,15,Fbut this was an element completely new
OL,16,Fto me.
OL,18,FI soon settled into the routine
OL,19,Fthough, and it all came rushing back
OL,20,Fto me.
