OL,3,CFrom the newsroom to the farm: A
OL,4,Cweekend lambing in Somerset
OL,6,FThe first task for the day was getting
OL,7,Fon top of everything from the night
OL,8,Fbefore.
OL,10,FOne of the first tasks was to cover
OL,11,Fthe new lambs' umbilical cord in
OL,12,Fiodine so it dries up and snaps off.
OL,13,FThis is to stop the lamb picking up
OL,14,Finfections.
