OL,3,CFrom the newsroom to the farm: A
OL,4,Cweekend lambing in Somerset
OL,6,FThen we gave everyone their breakfast.
OL,7,FYou need to be keeping the ewes fit
OL,8,Fand healthy so they produce plenty of
OL,9,Fmilk for the lambs so they get silage,
OL,10,Fwhich is like a nicer version of hay,
OL,11,Fand water. Those having or who had had
OL,12,Fthree lambs get some pellets too for
OL,13,Fextra nutrients.
OL,15,FAlongside all these jobs you can get
OL,16,Fdistracted by new arrivals. There are
OL,17,Fa few signs you can look out for to
OL,18,Ftell you a lamb is on the way. The ewe
OL,19,Fwill:
