OL,3,CFrom the newsroom to the farm: A
OL,4,Cweekend lambing in Somerset
OL,6,FAlthough I've helped on my family farm
OL,7,Fsince I could walk, there were many
OL,8,Fnew sides of lambing for me to pick up
OL,9,Fin Somerset with Rosie as my teacher.
OL,11,FThere are various adoption techniques
OL,12,Fyou can use if you have lots of
OL,13,Fsingles and lots of triplets. You want
OL,14,Feveryone to have two lambs because
OL,15,Fthat's all they can feed long-term.
