OL,3,CFrom the newsroom to the farm: A
OL,4,Cweekend lambing in Somerset
OL,6,FRosie introduced me to a new version
OL,7,Fwet adoption - using a bucket and
OL,8,Fsalt. You can make the ewe believe she
OL,9,Fhas two lambs instead of one by
OL,10,Fcovering the adopted lamb in the ewe's
OL,11,Fdelivery fluids and salt.
OL,13,FThe salt help the ewe want to lick the
OL,14,Flamb and form the important bond
OL,15,Fbetween then.
OL,17,FThe perks of outdoor lambing are that
OL,18,Fthe ewes can lamb themselves (most of
OL,19,Fthe time) and then you can leave them
OL,20,Fto it.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/8
