OL,3,CFrom the newsroom to the farm: A
OL,4,Cweekend lambing in Somerset
OL,6,FOccasionally the lambs need to be
OL,7,Fbrought indoors and it can prove
OL,8,Ftricky to catch them.
OL,10,FCatching the lambs and ewes outside
OL,11,Fwas exhausting and took a lot of
OL,12,Frunning. I do have a new found love of
OL,13,Fa crook now though.
OL,15,FYou can watch the extended version on
OL,16,FITV X .
